creator: KnowNOW Health
descriptionHtml: Easily Healthcare is a Direct Consumer, telemedicine platform that provides a simple at-home finger stick allergy test plus a video consultation with an allergy specialist for one low price. Find out if you are a good candidate for the Easily Allergy Toothpaste, which not only fights cavities and freshens your breath but can also make you less allergic to things like dust, pollen, and pets, just by brushing your teeth! This medicated toothpaste contains the same ingredients found in other products designed to desensitize you and make you less allergic, including allergy shots and allergy drops (SLIT), which have been shown to provide decades of symptom relief and less need for medication with only 3-5 years of treatment. Plus, with the money saved from buying less medication and missing less school or work, the treatment can pay for itself over time! Even though the treatment is not covered by insurance at this point, your health savings account (HSA, or Flex Spending) can help cover the cost. And the best part - If you and your doctor decide that the Easily Allergy Toothpaste is the right step for you, it can be sent directly to your home, so you can finally take care of your allergies ... Easily!
